                    <note>Taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="EMDA10">EMDA (HMML) 10, f. 224r.</ref>.</note>
                    <ab>ወነበሩ፡ በአሐቲ፡ ሀገር፡ ብዙኃን፡ ዓበይት፡ እለ፡ ሰምዑ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ድንግል፨ መንፈቆሙ፡ ዘሰምዑ፡ መንኰሱ፡ ወመንፈቆሙ፡ ተጸምዱ፡ በፍቅረ፡ ዚአሃ፨ ወመጽኡ፡ ካልአን፡ በቅንዓት፡ ከመ፡ ይውግርዎሙ፡ ወተኃብኡ፡ በምክረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ ፨</ab>
                </div>
            </div><!--  
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <note>Translated by Mehari Worku with Wendy Laura Belcher. <ref type="mss" corresp="EMDA10">EMDA (HMML) 10, s. 224b, col.1</ref>, in 2022. </note>
             <ab>In a town, a lot of aristocrats heard about a miracle of Our Lady Virgin Mary.
Half of those who had heard [about it] became monks and began [fervently] to serve Our Lady Mary’s love.
Then, envious others came to stone those aristocratic monks, but the Holy Spirit advised the monks to hide.
So, those envious others came to understand that the Holy Spirit and Our Lady Mary, the Holy Virgin, Mother of God had hidden those aristocratic monks.
So, they believed in the greatness of [Our Lady Mary,] the intercessor and merciful one.
My dear Lady Mary, save me, your servant Arkelieds, by your prayers, forever and ever. Amen.</ab>
